quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  30,11,Allah Taalaa hi makhlooq ki ibtida kerta hai phir wohi ussay doobara peda keray ga phir tum sab ussi ki taraf lotaye jaogay
  30,12,Aur jiss din qayamat qaeem hogi to gunehgaar heyrat zada reh jayen gay
  30,13,Aur inn kay tamam tar shareekon mein say aik bhi inn ka sifarshi na hoga aur (khud yeh bhi) apnay shareekon kay munkir ho jayen gay
  30,14,Aur jiss din qayamat qaeem hogi uss din (jamaten) alag alag hojayen gi
  30,15,Jo eman laa ker nek aemaal kertay rahey woh to jannat mein khush-o-khurram ker diyey jayen gay
  30,16,Aur jinhon ney kufur kiya tha aur humari aayaton ko aur aakhirat ki mulaqat ko jhoota theraya tha woh sab azab mein pakar ker hazir rakhay jayen gay
  30,17,Pus Allah Taalaa ki tasbeeh parha kero jab kay tum shaam kero aur jab subah kero
  30,18,Tamam tareefon kay laeeq aasman-o-zamin mein sirf wohi hai teesray pehar bhi aur zohar kay waqt bhi (uss ki pakeezgi biyan kero)
  30,19,(wohi) zinda ko murda say aur murda ko zinda say nikalta hai. Aur wohi zamin ko uss ki maut kay baad zinda kerta hai issi tarah tum (bhi) nikalay jao gay